headline: OREO Supports Youth Hockey with Second Year of 'OREO Stay Playful For All' Program Delivering Additional Grants Across Canada
summary: Today, OREO and the National Hockey League Players' Association (NHLPA) announced the second year of the 'OREO Stay Playful For All' program, which will deliver a total of $400,000 in donations to help make hockey more accessible to youth in Canada.
